e={{ transform: `translate(${pos.left}px, ${pos.top}px)` }}\n              className=\"absolute bg-red-600 text-white font-black py-3 px-6 whitespace-nowrap transition-transform duration-75 shadow-lg border-2 border-red-900 cursor-not-allowed\"\n            >\n              APPROVE PR\n            </button>\n        </div>\n        <p className=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 font-mono mt-8\">It\'s a feature, not a bug.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"
